        {
            "title": "亞洲匯市下跌,川普演說後避險情緒升溫推動美元反彈",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qH42.T07Wr9CVjwuSgRf6Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEE2C0N2_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 週四大多數亞洲貨幣下跌,而美元則出現反彈,此前美國總統唐納德·川普暗示中東衝突將進一步升級,促使資金重新流向避險資產。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元指數在亞洲交易時段上漲0.3%,從連續兩日的跌勢中反彈。截至美國東部時間23:39(北京時間11:39),美元指數期貨也上漲0.3%。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>川普演說暗示對伊朗戰爭進一步升級</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普表示,美國將在未來「兩到三週」加強對伊朗的軍事行動,但對停火前景幾乎未提供任何明確說明。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7640ec02-cc72-3810-b07f-d429bfc36c40-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這番言論打擊了本週稍早對衝突可能很快降溫的樂觀情緒,此前這種樂觀情緒曾對美元構成壓力,並支撐了區域貨幣。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價再次反彈,強化了通膨風險和謹慎的貨幣政策前景。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">韓元兌美元USD/KRW匯率跳升0.6%,而日圓兌美元USD/JPY上漲0.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">人民幣在岸匯率USD/CNY小幅上漲0.2%,而新加坡元USD/SGD上漲0.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度盧比USD/INR匯率基本持平於93.24盧比。該匯率在本週初曾觸及95.22盧比的歷史高點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度儲備銀行本週加強打擊外匯投機活動,禁止銀行向居民和非居民客戶提供盧比無本金交割遠期(NDF)合約,這是一種常被用來做空該貨幣的重要離岸工具。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>澳洲2月出口反彈</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管貿易數據強於預期,澳元兌美元AUD/USD匯率仍下跌0.5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳洲統計局數據顯示,該國2月貿易順差大幅擴大至56.9億澳元,遠高於預期,因出口增長4.9%,而進口下降3.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者現在將關注週五公布的美國關鍵勞動市場數據,特別是非農就業報告,以進一步了解聯準會的政策前景。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E5%8C%AF%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%BC%94%E8%AA%AA%E5%BE%8C%E9%81%BF%E9%9A%AA%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E5%8D%87%E6%BA%AB%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88-044557053.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-02 12:58:45",
