            "title": "原油直線拉升，布油升超4%突破106美元！特朗普警告將猛烈打擊伊朗",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周四，4月2日，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"特朗普\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:特朗普;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特朗普\">特朗普</a>警告將在未來數周對伊朗將開展猛烈打擊，原油價格直線拉升！倫敦布倫特原油期貨盤中一度突破106美元/桶，日內升幅達4%，創下近兩周新高。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"579\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KEwLyhxpQ5WBYRZLJYJ_cA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3OQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/acc639926d89004587b20f24d93af538\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">WTI原油期貨價格同步走高，一度站上104美元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"578\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YsZXuzZ_Rdw9xhNptD8xdw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3OA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/d844d113d26272f5175ae445105bb134\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息面上，香港時間4月2日早上9時（美東周三晚9點），美國總統特朗普就伊朗戰事發表全美電視講話。特朗普在講話中自行宣稱對伊朗戰事取得「快速、決定性、壓倒性勝利」，「未來兩到三周內，我們將對他們進行極其猛烈的打擊……同時，談判也在進行。」 此番表態釋放出「邊打邊談」的信號，進一步加劇了市場對中東局勢升級的擔憂，推動油價短線沖高。<br/><br/></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow m